quran[24]{c,v,t}:
  37,1,By those drawn up in ranks
  37,2,and by the warners crying warning
  37,3,and by the reciters of the Reminder
  37,4,your God is One
  37,5,Lord of the heavens and the earth and everything between them; Lord of the Easts
  37,6,We have adorned the lowest heaven with the beauty of the planets
  37,7,and guarded it against every defiant shaytan
  37,8,They cannot eavesdrop on the Highest Assembly and they are stoned from every side
  37,9,repelled with harshness — they will suffer eternal punishment —
  37,10,except for him who snatches a snippet and then is pursued by a piercing flame
  37,11,"Ask them for a fatwa: is it they who are stronger in structure or other things We have created? We created them from sticky clay"
  37,12,No wonder you are surprised as they laugh with scorn
  37,13,When they are reminded they do not pay heed
  37,14,When they see a Sign they only laugh with scorn
  37,15,"They say, ´This is just downright magic"
  37,16,When we are dead and turned to dust and bones will we then be raised up again alive
  37,17,And our earlier ancestors as well?´
  37,18,"Say: ´Yes, and you will be in a despicable state.´"
  37,19,There will be but one Great Blast and then their eyes will open
  37,20,"They will say, ´Alas for us! This is the Day of Reckoning!´"
  37,21,This is the Day of Decision you used to deny
  37,22,Assemble those who did wrong together with their associates and what they worshipped
  37,23,"besides Allah, and guide them to the Path of the Blazing Fire"
  37,24,And call them to a halt. They will be asked